{"tid":1089533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醉男消夜同人嘈 被肥瘦男爆樽","createTime":"2019-04-03T00:44:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T00:44:08.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8c0e6ac2b1a41b4434880943ff8f3dbeb581b2b9","tid":1089533,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T00:44:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XYO37pb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXYO37pb.png&h=a953ac3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n遇襲受傷男子送院。江寶龍攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/spHMkKj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FspHMkKj.png&h=1b811d14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n案發熟食中心。黎志偉攝<br />\n<br />\n黃大仙竹園南邨華園樓熟食中心（俗稱冬菇亭），凌晨1時27分，一名姓馬47歲男子消夜，疑酒醉與兩名男子爭執，被人用玻璃樽扑頭襲擊，頭破血流，嘴角及臉部亦受傷，兇徒傷人逃去。警方到場在附近兜截沒有發現，傷者送院治理。現正追緝兩名肥身材及瘦身材兇徒。"}]}